                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> What do you know the shift by? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> By the name marked on it—the prisoner was with me nearly two months—she never slept in my house.</p>
